{"tid":2238731,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[大浪灣一日遊]條條大浪通石澳","createTime":"2020-10-11T11:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T12:25:18.000Z","uid":64601,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e3c36676f04dff33db03596c93f5b1c0eec6f4b3","tid":2238731,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T11:14:55.000Z","msg":"今日主題係大浪灣，路線係小西灣-大浪灣-石澳，行咗四個鐘左右，唔難行、景正、舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n朝早十一點柴灣等，搭47小巴入小西灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ibd74wR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fibd74wR.jpg&h=d146daa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小西灣個view幾正，要浪漫有浪漫，要殘暴可以推鳩人落海<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日路程：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3jrp6Me.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3jrp6Me.png&h=2f5094b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hikingtrailhk.appspot.com/s/k1oNAw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhikingtrailhk.appspot.com%2Fs%2Fk1oNAw&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=aa67708a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hikingtrailhk.appspot.com/s/k1oNAw</a><br />\ndl 香港遠足路線/hiking trail app可以睇返我今日路線。唔想行太耐嘅可以行到大浪灣就走，想行少啲嘅可以行小西灣，再想少啲嘅可以返屋企瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[多圖注意！]一開始係行龍躍徑，難免多老嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/10/11/185250_40838e3fc84ef2afb17a605bfbd1299c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F10%2F11%2F185250_40838e3fc84ef2afb17a605bfbd1299c.jpg&h=1876a92e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上樓梯落樓梯少不免，但唔算多，以一開始為主，行半粒鐘左右就有海景睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/10/11/185357_8ce9dd0ce8143ec7b289b8cec4bad214.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F10%2F11%2F185357_8ce9dd0ce8143ec7b289b8cec4bad214.jpg&h=9cc50d77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無敵大海，好快就會同佢接觸到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5Fuys9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5Fuys9.jpg&h=b07098fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知做乜鬼有間廢屋，唔知係咪姑婆屋嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mEXgXVa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmEXgXVa.jpg&h=3a69983e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n涼風輕輕吹過漸馬丁露乜鳩~<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yr7QhWq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYr7QhWq.jpg&h=6b336d90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/10/11/190104_c2e3cec398123b4668c362b6754fe322.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F10%2F11%2F190104_c2e3cec398123b4668c362b6754fe322.jpg&h=1ebc002b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到大浪灣就行落去石刻度，可以親近大海<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />滄海一聲笑，笑鳩呂麗搖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x3s46Qe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx3s46Qe.jpg&h=6593fa45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/10/11/190254_40e7e9d6a22d3a79b03a4de5fa64b8b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F10%2F11%2F190254_40e7e9d6a22d3a79b03a4de5fa64b8b0.jpg&h=3c466945&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行多陣就會到海灘，泳客已走光<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BNB9ywd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBNB9ywd.jpg&h=f742e866&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wkHXHpA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwkHXHpA.jpg&h=5fcd733d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行到士多都兩點半，係時候食飯，但啲嘢食太劣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />飲下酒仲寫意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VcairRS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVcairRS.jpg&h=d491c2c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最尾行埋去石澳就完事了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tvjbMR3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtvjbMR3.jpg&h=4a133131&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k4jWdw4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk4jWdw4.jpg&h=8f329cfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n總結：成程好c服，一陣陣海風吹嚟，好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一年後或者翻兜<br />\n<br />\n[私人影集]隔離係平路，好安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MfUnTxY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMfUnTxY.jpg&h=1a7c09c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"512c94375ca614ac13b25646150f6df292477661","tid":2238731,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T11:15:22.000Z","msg":"0/10"},{"pid":"8c6d78e878a8a585e375f169d6c19907bf5a87cd","tid":2238731,"uid":3545,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T11:15:42.000Z","msg":"健康 10/10"},{"pid":"6e563fb4d94fe83ade8cc92c893b23390b5a5794","tid":2238731,"uid":312193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T11:15:59.000Z","msg":"枝酒就咁睇張相都幾唔好飲下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3246e675febc9fbb6dd5b7f412f148774673ecda","tid":2238731,"uid":64601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"512c94375ca614ac13b25646150f6df292477661","tid":2238731,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T11:15:22.000Z","msg":"0/10"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T11:16:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />行山啫"},{"pid":"5b8ebdccc58c698b87b2e0e086d9ec5409e2dd4f","tid":2238731,"uid":136416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T11:16:34.000Z","msg":"正<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>［20號就截！］德國聯署逐步圖文教學 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2237513\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2237513</a><br />\n有12人受緊苦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"8df5d29981ef2af236c317bf06f2e66c5936ad98","tid":2238731,"uid":190879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T11:16:37.000Z","msg":"健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi